OL,5, Around 100 people denied fast-tracked  
OL,6, disability benefits for terminal       
OL,7, illness died challenging the decision. 
OL,9,FCurrently, patients can access benefits
OL,10,Fmore quickly if their clinician says   
OL,11,Fthey have six months or less to live.  
OL,13,FIn July the government promised to     
OL,14,Fextend that to 12 months. Critics said 
OL,15,Fit did not go far enough.              
OL,17,F"Our priority is dealing with people's 
OL,18,Fclaims quickly and compassionately,"   
OL,19,Fthe Department for Work and Pensions   
OL,20,F(DWP) said.                            
